 <item> <title>U.S. Education Secretary DeVos Issues Letter to Chief State School Officers</title>
 <link>https://www.ed.gov/news/press-releases/us-education-secretary-devos-issues-letter-chief-state-school-officers</link>
 <description>In a letter delivered today to chief state school officers, U.S. Secretary of Education Betsy DeVos provided clarity on Every Student Succeeds Act (ESSA) implementation, in light of the actions related to the postponement of the accountability regulations and the Congressional Review Act.</description>
